Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.82,0:55:55.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}奇妙的风拂过
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.95,0:56:00.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}世界开始绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.81,0:56:11.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}无论何时何刻
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.44,0:56:13.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}城市里都洋溢着美好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.87,0:56:17.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}“愿意相信”的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.95,0:56:20.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}便是我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.93,0:56:23.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}今天　要怎么样　该怎么样做
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.96,0:56:27.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}才能前进呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.46,0:56:29.29,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur.8}(怎么样做呢？)
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.31,0:56:30.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}但是　成天纠结　只是纠结的话
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.52,0:56:34.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}不是“我的风格”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.74,0:56:34.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur.8}(Ha-ah)
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.12,0:56:40.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}“反复试错”的每天我也最爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.24,0:56:40.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur.8}(让我们朝着梦想前进)
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.10,0:56:46.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}我想用双手携着“心动”　将光芒传递
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.60,0:56:49.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}任风吹拂　与风同行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.99,0:56:53.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}全都交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.51,0:56:53.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur.8}(Ha　Ha-ah)
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.40,0:56:56.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}无论是怎样的“黑暗”
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.52,0:57:02.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}有大家都在身边就不会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.56,0:57:03.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur.8}(Ha-ah)
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.87,0:57:05.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}看　未来也在
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.69,0:57:06.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur.8}(Ha-ah)
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.79,0:57:08.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.19,0:57:12.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur.8}(Ha-ah　Ha-ah)
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.47,0:57:19.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur.8}(La la la la la)
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.72,0:57:23.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}无论哪一刻都希望
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.31,0:57:25.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}自己变得更加坦诚
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.83,0:57:29.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}想要多多在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.89,0:57:32.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}开心地笑
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.69,0:57:35.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}总是被说是
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.84,0:57:39.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}相当单纯　十分天真的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.33,0:57:41.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur.8}(为什么呢？)
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.19,0:57:42.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}多么无邪　非常纯粹
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.34,0:57:51.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}像太阳一样温暖又闪亮的　宝贵的感情
