Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.77,0:58:20.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.17,0:58:30.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}相信梦想　悄然出发
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.87,0:58:39.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur.8}朝着所见天空的彼岸前进
